snippet.textDisplay: I'm a 72 year old British male who discovered Abida Parveen while working in India some 2 years ago.  Although already very familiar with the music of the Sub-continent, including her so-called predecessor, Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan, Abida P simply blew me out of the water, and I remain a huge fan.  But this particular track is particularly special and makes me almost wheep with emotion everytime I hear it.
